---
// Componente informativo para el panel izquierdo del login
---
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8 w-full max-w-md mx-auto py-16 animate-fade-in">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-full p-4 mb-2 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-105 animate-fade-in-up">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2" /><path d="M16 3v4M8 3v4M3 9h18" /></svg>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white animate-fade-in-up">MediSchedule</h1>
    <p class="text-lg font-medium text-white opacity-90 animate-fade-in-up max-w-xs">Tu salud es nuestra prioridad. Agenda tus citas fácilmente y gestiona tu historial médico de forma segura.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 w-full mt-4">
    <div class="bg-blue-400 bg-opacity-90 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col items-center shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 cursor-pointer min-h-[100px]">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-1">Agendamiento fácil</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white opacity-90">Agenda tus citas en pocos clics.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-blue-400 bg-opacity-90 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col items-center shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 cursor-pointer min-h-[100px]">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-1">Historial médico</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white opacity-90">Accede a tus registros médicos en cualquier momento.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-blue-400 bg-opacity-90 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col items-center shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 cursor-pointer min-h-[100px]">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-1">Seguro y privado</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white opacity-90">Tus datos están protegidos con seguridad de nivel industrial.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-blue-400 bg-opacity-90 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col items-center shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300 cursor-pointer min-h-[100px]">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-white mb-1">Notificaciones instantáneas</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white opacity-90">Recibe recordatorios de tus próximas citas.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <style>
    .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 1s ease; }
    .animate-fade-in-up { animation: fadeInUp 1s ease; }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
    @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  </style>
</div> 